00:51:45.180 --> 00:51:51.630
&gt;&gt; Male #1: Thank you for coming. I found
your book very interesting, how you look at

00:51:51.630 --> 00:51:56.279
things they did in the past like slavery and
recreational cat burning that we just think

00:51:56.279 --> 00:52:00.480
as unthinkable. Hundred years from now what
do we do that they are going to look back

00:52:00.480 --> 00:52:03.089
on and say how could they possibly have done
that.

00:52:03.089 --> 00:52:07.900
&gt;&gt; Steven: It's quite possible that our treatment
