00:52:21.490 --> 00:52:26.720
on what happens they might consider the indifference
to the state of environment and its effects

00:52:26.720 --> 00:52:32.760
on future generations. Those are three possibilities.
What we're seeing now, by the way, catching

00:52:32.760 --> 00:52:39.089
it in the act of something that was formerly
