00:53:01.930 --> 00:53:07.640
these values that we value and yet they've
been around a very long time by your own statistics

00:53:07.640 --> 00:53:10.460
don't seem to show much correlation to anything.

00:53:10.460 --> 00:53:14.900
&gt;&gt; Steven: Most values of most religions are
